Project Summary: Meeting Intelligence Hub

We’re building a smart meeting analysis platform that processes both meeting conversations and presentation slides to generate summaries, decisions, and actionable tasks.

Instead of manually reviewing long meetings, users get clear insights, structured outputs, and assigned responsibilities, all in one place.

